\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 17. P. arguteserrata} Vved. in Schischkin & Bobrov, {\i Fl. URSS}{\b  22}: 809 (1955). Like {\b 16} but stems up to 30 cm; leaves pinnatifid, with segments toothed or entire; bracts villous; calyx villous, usually tinged with violet; corolla pinkish-lilac, with lower lip shorter than or equalling the upper; capsule broadly oblong.{\i  Open woods. C. Ural}. Rs (C). ({\i Siberia, Mongolia}.)
